- Increased reach
- Can use Staff, Red, and Cyan styles

Force Powers:
- Jump (3)
- Push (3)
- Pull (3)
- Grip (2)
- Sense (2)
- Force Block (3)
- Force Focus (2)

~Character Option 1: Darth Maul - Former apprentice of Darth Sidious, Maul is a relentless killer - whose single-minded hatred motivates and sustains him.
~Character Option 2: Second Sister - Once the Jedi Padawan Trilla Suduri, the Second Sister was an Inquisitor hunting remnants of the Jedi Order after the Purge.
~Character Option 3: Darth Zannah - The successor to Darth Bane who murdered him to carry on his teaching of 'The Rule of Two.'
~Character Option 4: Darth Maladi - A member of Krayt's one sith order.
~Character Option 5: Grand Inquisitor - A Pau'an Jedi Temple Guard turned Jedi Hunter."
